Upon entering this home is the formal dining room, then the living room showcasing a fireplace while the kitchen has a breakfast bar and breakfast nook. The primary bedroom includes the primary bathroom with dual sinks, a garden tub, separate shower and walk-in closet. The two secondary bedrooms, secondary bathroom and laundry room make up the rest of the home while the fenced in backyard offers a large covered patio. This home is in proximity to TX-99!
